title: Digital Adoption Platform 
---
#H1 Digital Adoption Tools 
Digital adoption tools are low-code applications that enable writers to add overlays of content to an application, without needing access to the application's source code, and without a developer needing to load content into the application on the writer's behalf.  If you've downloaded any kind of app, you'll probably have seen a guided tour explaining how to get started, exposing new features or getting past the initial empty state. 
